social_posts.post_text: Healed lines, fresh color on these stomach pieces for @keepitcutale 🖤
Great Blue Heron for @sarahfran17 💙
Little magical piece for Jodie 🌙💙

In full Christmas spirit over here ❤️🎄🦌 Seattle is super icy today so that means staying indoors, baking gingerbread cookies and binging Christmas movies with @matthildebrandtattoo and the doggies 🥰🐶 hope everyone has a wonderful weekend surrounded with love ❤️
One session shot of a lovely deer for Rachel 🦌🧡
New Year’s Eve came with an extra special surprise this year 😍😍😍❤️ I love you so much @matthildebrandtattoo ❤️ I can’t wait to marry you and have endless adventures forever 🥰

I just want to thank all of my clients from the bottom of my heart ❤️ You guys are so awesome and make my job the most fun! 2022 was incredible to say the least, but you all really make every year so special. So many of my clients turn into friends and family and I cherish every single one of you no matter whether you’ve gotten one piece from me, or you’ve been getting tattooed by me for over ten years. You’re all the best and I’m so grateful for the love and support all these years 🥹❤️
Part one of two for @seatay of her cutie malinois 🖤 next pup on the other side very soon 🥰
@rylixiou got me using all sorts of bright colors to do this super cool multiple eyed animal sleeve for her and I had so much fun! 💙👁️👄👁️💜
Added a reaper and some florals to fill Bianca’s side a little while back 🖤💀 fresh color/healed lines in this photo, other pieces not by me.
I’ve been slacking on posting lately but this piece on @lexitayylorr I did recently was so much fun!! And she is just the sweetest 🥰🖤
Healed heart mace on @inkdbydmo who is not only the sweetest, but incredibly talented as well ⚔️ its always an honor to tattoo another tattooer 🖤 (lettering not by me)
Philosophers & Florals on Anna 🖤 Kierkegaard • Nietzsche • Sartre • Beauvoir 🖤

Thank you so much again @salvage_arts for including me in such an amazing show!! Here’s some before and after resin shots since that was a learning experience to say the least 🤪 “flighted fervor” oil on wood.
Full sleeve for CC 🖤 mostly healed, some fresh, with a little rework on existing crystals ✨
Added a final couple flowers to complete this project on @thebrowcowgirl 🖤 (lettering not by me).
Got to finish @andywillwin ‘s nature sleeve recently. Mostly healed/some fresh 🍁
Aztec Jaguar for @k.kittyz 🖤🐆
Happy Fourth of July!! 🇺🇸❤️ hope everyone has a safe and fun holiday 🥰

Had so much fun doing this meaningful piece for @jen_puravida of a representation of her nana as a goddess ✨ Jen also makes beautiful handmade jewelry so definitely go check out her shop! @purelifejewelry 🩵
Progress shots of @finding_taradise arm 🐌🩵 snail and berries are fresh, Luna moth and Butterfly healed 🌙🌞🖤
Muted vintage floral sleeve for Natasha 🌿🖤🏵️
Sacred Heart for @k.kittyz 🖤🔥
One heck of a challenging project but I’m so stoked on how this all came together on @crt_sportscards ⚾️🐻‍❄️ thank you Chris for your dedication and trust!!
The cutest little storybook owl filler piece for @hairbycelina.guru 🦉🍄🌿
Peep the chipmunk socks 👀 made a little video of these skateboards from the @salvage_arts show awhile back 🖤
First of many cute critters going on Jodie’s magical forest sleeve, lines are healed/color is fresh, background coming in future sessions 🥰🦌🍄
▕⃝⃤ Harry Potter Lantern on @alananicole83 🖤
⚔️Athena ⚔️ themed leg for Katie 🖤 knee and ankle are fresh, everything else healed.
🍂 All the fall vibes with this piece for @crushing_my_next_chapter 🍁

👻 I’m so excited to share that we are back at it again with another spooky season of doing 31 drawings during the month of October! 🎃 The lovely @haleybearstattoo , @otrtattoos and myself will each be posting a drawing a day on our stories for the entire month, starting tomorrow! 🖤 Follow along to see what we come up with for each theme of the day🕸️🕷️
Finished up this peacock sleeve for @twisted_coil 🦚 so happy with how this turned out 🖤
